data.enText: a small flat block, often made of wood, marked on one side with two groups of dots representing numbers, used for playing games
a game played with a set of dominoes , in which players take turns to put them onto a table

tr: a small rectangular block used in playing the game of dominoes
the face of each block has two equal areas that can bear 0 to 6 dots
a mask covering the upper part of the face but with holes for the eyes
a loose hooded cloak worn with a half mask as part of a masquerade costume

value.def: Dominoes are small rectangular blocks marked with two groups of spots on one side. They are used for playing various games.
Dominoes is a game in which players put dominoes onto a table in turn.
value.tran: 西洋骨牌戏;多米诺骨牌戏
